@startuml
title Containers - Restaurante Manager

node "Navegador / Cliente" as Browser {
  component "SPA Restaurante Manager\nHTML/CSS/JS\n(public/)" as SPA
}

node "Servidor Backend\nNode.js + Express\n(server.js)" as Backend {
  component "Módulo de Autenticação\n(routes/auth.js, authMiddleware.js)" as Auth
  component "Serviço de Dados\n(db.js)" as Data
}

database "SQLite\n(database.sqlite)" as DB

Browser --> Backend : HTTP/HTTPS\nRequisições GET/POST\nCookies HttpOnly (JWT)
Backend --> DB : Driver sqlite3\nCRUD em users

SPA --> Auth : /api/auth/login\n/api/auth/logout\n/api/auth/register\n/api/auth/users

@enduml
